Cell[TextData[{
 "Now we shall decompose the second term of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "(", "T", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a1bdfc26-15e0-4f46-90b5-9f035445828d"],
 " into Euler angles to represent it as sequence of YZY pulses. The main \
motivation here is to explore how ",
